title: Preachers Of LA Season 2
description:
Preachers.of.LA.S02E01.x264-NoGRP
A community event is planned by the preachers in the Season 2 premiere. Included: Jay confronts Deitrick over wedding issues, and Bishop Ron clashes with Bishop Noel.

Preachers Of LA S02E02 HDTV x264-NoGRP
Tensions boil over as a showdown erupts over the status of Bishop Noel and Loretta's relationship; Christy defends Jay's decision to confront Deitrick; Jay attempts to save a young drug addict's life.

Preachers.Of.LA.S02E03.HDTV.x264-NoGRP
Sparks fly as Jay confronts Deitrick about the wedding; Loretta faces off with First Lady LaVette at Dominique's Sip N See

Preachers.Of.LA.S02E04.HDTV.x264-NoGRP
Ron and LaVette Gibson, Wayne and Myesha Chaney and psychologist Thema Bryant-Davis are the guests on the show.

Preachers.Of.L.A.S02E05.Prodigal.Son.WS.DSR.x264-[NY2]
Pastor Jay has a difficult decision to make after his troubled son returns home. Pastor Wayne makes a big decision whilst Deitrick puts some unwanted pressure on Dominique. 

Preachers Of L.A. S02E06 Sins Of The Father WS DSR x264-NY2
Deitrick makes his way to Detroit to find some difficult information about his biological father. Bishop McClendon looks back on his childhood.

Preachers Of L.A. S02E07 Restoration WS DSR x264-NY2
After being dramatically restored by his old congregation in Detroit, Dietrick decides to reconcile with Jay; Bishop Gibson attempts to reunite his family; Pastor Wayne struggles with a very personal decision.

Preachers Of L.A. S02E08 My Brothers Keeper WS DSR x264-NY2
Things get heated when Pastor Chaney tries to mend severed family ties; Bishop Jones throws Loretta a birthday party, and his gift leaves her speechless; Ron Gibson helps an ex-con begin a new life.

Preachers.Of.L.A.S02E09.Meet.The.Godparents.WS.DSR.x264-[NY2
Bishop Gibson and Pastor Haizlip organize a gang summit. Pastor Chaney adds a new pastor to his conference. 

Preachers Of L.A. S02E10 Bouncing Back WS DSR x264-NY2
Deitrick reaches out to fellow gospel artist Kevin Terry; Myesha deals with the serious issue of sex trafficking at her Hiding Behind the Lipstick conference; Christy Haizlip does some soul-searching.
